; HelloWorld - A minimal OPS5 program
; Demonstrates: literalize, make, write, variable binding

; === Class definitions ===
(literalize planet name size)

; === Initial data ===
(make planet ^name Earth ^size Large)
(make planet ^name Mars ^size Small)

; === Production rules ===

(p hello
    (planet ^name <name>)
    -->
    (write |Hello | <name>))
